premise_source_doc_sentence: Anabelle is a feminine given name , and may refer to :
Anabelle Langlois  (  born 1981  )  , a Canadian pairs figure skater
Anabelle Prawerman  (  born 1963  )  , a French beach volleyball player
Anabelle Rodriguez , a Puerto Rican lawyer
The variation Annabelle may refer to :
Annabelle , a 2014 American supernatural horror film directed by John R. Leonetti .
Annabelle Wallis , an English actress , who stars in the 2014 movie , Annabelle .
See other references at Annabel , which includes Annabelle .
Annabel or Annabelle may refer to :
At its peak , there were 18 Annabelle 's units in five states .
Annabelle , a variety of wild hydrangea
Today there is one remaining Annabelle 's location in New Bern , NC .
